quran[7{c,v,t}:
3,23,"tum ne dekha nahi jin logon ko kitaab ke ilm mein se kuch hissa mila hai, unn ka haal kya hai? unhen jab kitaab Ellahi ki taraf bulaya jata hai taakay woh unn ke darmain faisla kere, to un mein se aik fareeq is se pehlu tehi karta hai aur is faislay ki taraf anay se mun phair jata hai"
3,24,"un ka yeh tarz amal is wajah se hai ke woh kehte hain"" aatish dozakh to hamein miss taq nah kere gi aur agar dozakh ki saza hum ko miley gi bhi to bas chand roz"" unn ke khud sakhta aqeedon ne unn ko apne deen ke muamlay mein barri ghalat fehmiyon mein daal rakha hai"
3,25,magar kya banay gi unn par jab hum inhen uss roz jama karen ge jis ka aana yakeeni hai? is roz har shakhs ko is ki kamaai ka badla poora poora day diya jaayegaa aur kisi par zulm nah hoga
3,26,"kaho! khudaaya! mulk ke maalik! to jisay chahay, hukoomat day aur jisay chahay, chean le jisay chahay, izzat bakhshay aur jis ko chahay, zaleel kar day bhalai tairay ikhtiyar mein hai bay shak to har cheez par Qadir hai"
3,27,"raat ko din mein pirota howa le aata hai aur din ko raat mein jandaar mein se be jaan ko nkalta hai aur be jaan mein se jandaar ko aur jisay chahta hai, be hisaab rizaq deta hai"
3,28,momnin ahal imaan ko chore kar kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq aur dost hargiz nah banayen jo aisa kere ga is ka Allah se koi talluq nahi haan yeh maaf hai ke tum un ke zulm se bachney ke liye bzahir aisa tarz amal ikhtiyar kar jao magar Allah tumhe apne aap se darata hai aur tumhe isi ki taraf palat kar jana hai
3,29,"ae Nabi Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! logon ko khabardaar kar do ke tumahray dilon mein jo kuch hai, ussay khuwa tum chupao ya zahir karo, Allah behar haal usay jaanta hai, zameen o aasman ki koi cheez is ke ilm se bahar nahi hai aur uss ka Iqtidaar har cheez par haawi hai"
